Install Lingua::EN::SimilarNames::Levenshtein either using the cpan shell like this:

        cpan Lingua::EN::SimilarNames::Levenshtein

    OR by downloading and extracting the tarball from:

        http://search.cpan.org/dist/Lingua-EN-Similar-Names-Levenshtein

    cd to the extracted directory Lingua-EN-SimilarNames-Levenshtein-x.xx/ then run:

	    * perl Makefile.PL
	    * make test
	    * make install

